A(Acute dyspnea) --&gt; B(["Lung sliding? &lt;br/&gt; Lung pulse? &lt;br/&gt; B-lines?"])

B --&gt;|Any| C[Pneumothorax excluded]

B --&gt;|None| D([Lung point?])

D --&gt; |No| E["Pneumothorax likely &lt;br/&gt; confirm with CXR/CT"]

D --&gt; |Yes| F[Pneumothorax confirmed]

C --&gt; G(["B-lines? &lt;br/&gt; Effusion? &lt;br/&gt; Condensation?"])

G --&gt; |No| H["Normal pattern: &lt;br/&gt; Normal, PE, asthma, COPD"]

G --&gt; |Yes| I["Compare patterns for: &lt;br/&gt; Pneumonia, &lt;br/&gt; cardiogenic edema, &lt;br/&gt; isolated effusion"]

I --&gt; J(["Consider cardiac US for &lt;br/&gt; evaluation of cardiogenic component"])

